  <h2>🛡️ Vulnerabilities</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>CISA adds Linux kernel (CVE-2025-38352), Android Runtime (CVE-2025-48543), and Sitecore deserialization (CVE-2025-53690) flaws to KEV after active exploitation <a href="https://www.cisa.gov/news-events/alerts/2025/09/04/cisa-adds-three-known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
    <li>TP-Link confirms unpatched zero-day in CWMP implementation on multiple routers, enabling RCE; patches released for EU devices <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-tp-link-zero-day-surfaces-as-cisa-warns-other-flaws-are-exploited/" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
  </ul>

