    <li>SentinelLabs & Validin uncover Lazarus-linked “Contagious Interview” campaign exploiting CTI platforms and targeting crypto professionals <a href="https://www.sentinelone.com/labs/contagious-interview-threat-actors-scout-cyber-intel-platforms-reveal-plans-and-ops/" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
